<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Casos Clínicos - NurseCore</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#f0fdf4] font-sans text-slate-800 flex min-h-screen">

    <aside id="sidebar" class="w-64 bg-[#86efac] text-emerald-950 flex flex-col justify-between shadow-lg flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="p-6">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-wider text-emerald-900">NurseCore</h1>
            <p class="text-xs text-emerald-700 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold">Panel Académico</p>
            <nav class="space-y-1">
                <a href="dashboard-estudiante.html" class="sidebar-item-light hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl transition block py-2.5 px-4 font-medium">🏠 Dashboard</a>
                
                <a href="#" class="block py-3 px-4 rounded-xl bg-white/40 font-bold active-item shadow-sm text-emerald-950">📚 Casos Clínicos</a>
                
                <a href="#" class="sidebar-item-light hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl transition block py-2.5 px-4 font-medium">📝 Reg. de Prácticas</a>
                
                <div class="border-t border-emerald-900/10 my-4"></div>
                
                <a href="guias.html" class="sidebar-item-light hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl transition block py-2.5 px-4 font-medium">📖 Guías</a>
                <a href="evaluaciones.html" class="sidebar-item-light hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl transition block py-2.5 px-4 font-medium">✅ Evaluaciones</a>
                
                <a href="perfil-estudiante.html" class="sidebar-item-light hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl transition block py-2.5 px-4 font-medium mt-4">👤 Mi Perfil Académico</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border-t border-emerald-900/10 text-xs font-semibold text-emerald-800">
            Modo: Prácticas Académicas
        </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col">
        
        <header class="h-20 bg-[#14532d] flex items-center justify-between px-8 text-white shadow-md">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-wide text-emerald-200">Módulo de Casos Clínicos</h1>
                <p class="text-sm text-emerald-300/80">Resolución, análisis y escenarios simulados</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="dashboard-estudiante.html" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 transition text-white text-xs font-bold px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl border border-emerald-500/30">
                    ← Volver al Dashboard
                </a>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="p-8 space-y-8">
            
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-between items-center">
                <div class="w-full sm:w-72">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Buscar caso por diagnóstico..." class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-xs font-medium focus:outline-none focus:border-emerald-500">
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                    <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Todos (3)</span>
                    <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">En Progreso</span>
                    <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg">Pendientes</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[250px]">
                    <div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Completado</span>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400">ID: #CC-081</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 leading-snug">Insuficiencia Cardíaca Congestiva</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Paciente varón de 65 años con disnea progresiva y edema de miembros inferiores.</p>
                        
                        <div class="mt-4 space-y-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-slate-600">
                            <p>🩺 <strong>Área:</strong> Medicina Interna</p>
                            <p>⏱️ <strong>Duración estimada:</strong> 45 min</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="w-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 font-bold py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs mt-4 hover:bg-slate-200 transition">
                        Revisar Historial Evaluado
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[250px]">
                    <div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                            <span class="bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">En Progreso</span>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400">ID: #CC-094</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 leading-snug">Cetoacidosis Diabética</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Paciente femenina de 22 años con diabetes tipo 1, presenta respiración de Kussmaul y deshidratación severa.</p>
                        
                        <div class="mt-4 space-y-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-slate-600">
                            <p>🩺 <strong>Área:</strong> Urgencias / Emergencias</p>
                            <p>⏱️ <strong>Duración estimada:</strong> 60 min</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="w-full bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-600 text-slate-950 font-black py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs mt-4 transition">
                        Continuar Simulación →
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[250px]">
                    <div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                            <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Pendiente</span>
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400">ID: #CC-102</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 leading-snug">Apendicitis Aguda Pediátrica</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Paciente masculino de 9 años con dolor en fosa ilíaca derecha, náuseas y signo de Blumberg positivo.</p>
                        
                        <div class="mt-4 space-y-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-slate-600">
                            <p>🩺 <strong>Área:</strong> Pediatría / Cirugía</p>
                            <p>⏱️ <strong>Duración estimada:</strong> 40 min</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="w-full bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs mt-4 hover:bg-slate-800 transition">
                        Iniciar Caso Clínico
                    </button>
                </div>

            </div>

        </main>
    </div>

    <script>
        // ESCUDO DE SEGURIDAD GENERAL DE NURSECORE
        if (!localStorage.getItem("usuarioLogueado") || localStorage.getItem("tipoUsuario") !== "estudiante") {
            window.location.href = "login.html";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
